{"type":null,"faqId":13103,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02 使用数据业务上网经常掉线，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请在移动网络信号较强的地方上网。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>在<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>移动网络</b>，勾选<b>始终连接数据业务</b>复选框。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37739\" /> \n<p>\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">向网络运营商咨询手机的接入点名称（</span><span>APN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）参数是否正确。在<b>移动网络</b>中，点击<b>接入点名称（</b></span><b><span>APN</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，可以查看当前使用的接入点。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=37740\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若尝试以上方法后仍然不能解决问题，请备份重要数据，将手机恢复出厂设置，重新连接。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4066","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1402018263000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":571,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}